summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Eastern Avenue from North Fiftieth Street to the South line of Smith's University Add. et al in the City of Seattle, by grading under Ordinance No. 21535, creating Local Improvement District No. 2136 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
